1357459223.text: "The second pathway involves an intermediate step mediated by cleavage of the pro apoptotic Bcl-2 family member Bid, triggering Bcl-2 family members Bax and Bak to orchestrate mitochondrial outer membrane permeabilization (MOMP) to initiate the intrinsic apoptotic pathway (XREF_FIG)."
